				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Luxembourg CNS quota system\n\nPatients track their usage of CNS psychology session codes:\n- **SP01** — first 12 sessions (fully reimbursed)\n- **SP02** — next 12 sessions (partially reimbursed)\n- **SP03** — beyond 24 sessions (not reimbursed)\n\nThe `nextCodeActe` method on a patient automatically selects the right code. You can inspect a patient's quota status directly — it shows remaining sessions per code."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-04-01T00:03:12.183998+02:00"
					}
